opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of July, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Writ of Mandamus as Motion to Compel” and the Application for Leave to Supplement are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
